duct Information. Levatol (penbutolol)." Reed and Carnrick  (2001):|"Product Information. Coreg (carvedilol)." SmithKline Beecham  (2001):|Frishman WH "Carvedilol." N Engl J Med 339 (1998):  1759-65|Braunwald E, Hauser SL, Kasper DL, Fauci AS, Isselbacher KJ, Longo DL, Martin JB, eds., Wilson JD "Harrison''s Principles of Internal Medicine." New York, NY: McGraw-Hill Health Professionals Division  (1998):|"Product Information. Bystolic (nebivolol)." Forest Pharmaceuticals  (2007):', 'DDInter', 0);
